[[Rotaract]]: a service club for young men and women aged 18 to 30 with around 185,000 members in 7,000 clubs in 163 countries. Rotaract clubs are either community or university based, and they are sponsored by a local Rotary club. This makes them true "partners in service" and key members of the family of Rotary.<ref>http://www.rotary.org/en/studentsandyouth/youthprograms/rotaract/pages/ridefault.aspx</ref>
